            <sentence id="9.1">[Information automatically included from LibreOffice]
Locale: es
Module: StartModule
[Information guessed from browser]
OS: Linux (All)
OS is 64bit: yes</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="10">
            <sentence id="10.1">Reset User Profile?No</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
